subject: Track and Field
lead_paragraph: Tennessee’s Phoebe Wright fended off a late challenge from Villanova’s Sheila Reid to lead the Volunteers to their second straight victory in the women’s 6,000-meter race at the Penn Relays in Philadelphia.
